nodes.text: Lodge of the Order of the Canted Circle

The Lodge of the Order of the Canted Circle was located in the Fobosi District and served as the headquarters of the Order of the Canted Circle. In 52 BBY, during Larsh Hill's initiation ceremony, an attack was launched against several members of the Order by assassins hired by Pax Teem, though the main target had been Hego Damask.
